We’re always looking for ways to improve our customers’ experience by offering tools and services to fit their lifestyles. In the latest update:
• Now you can register on GroupNet for Plan Members through our GroupNet Mobile app.
Bug Fixes

IMPORTANT: Did you recently update your GroupNet Mobile app to our latest version (1.8.1)? You will experience an error when trying to open the app for the first time after the app is updated. To access these great new features please uninstall the app, download it again and re-install it.
